JSLint Reporter
Node.js wrapper for JSLint (http://jslint.com) and JSHint (http://www.jshint.com)


Usage:

  $ node wrapper.js [options] <filepath>

(use `node wrapper.js --upgrade` to generate jslint.js alongside wrapper.js)


Options:

  --<name>[=<value>]
    names as per http://www.jslint.com/lint.html#options
    (e.g. "--vars --predef=foo,bar,baz --maxlen=80")

  --jshint
    use JSHint instead of JSLint

  --upgrade
    download latest version of JSLint

  --verbose
    display additional information

  --version
    display version numbers for both JSLint Reporter and JSLint

  --help
    display this usage information
